RE:Your Account #: {!Product__c.CCS_Client_ID__c}
Customer Name: {!Product__r.Customer__r.Name}
Customer Account #: {!Product__c.Name}
Original Creditor: {!Product__c.Originating_Creditor__c}

Pursuant to the notice received by the Creditor, the above customer has applied for a debt management program with your office.

You are seeking the Creditor’s approval to this debt liquidation under the following proposal:
CCS Proposed Payment Amount: {!Product__c.CCS_Proposed_Payment_Amount__c}
Proposed Payment Amount: {!Product__c.Proposed_Payment_Amount__c}
Payment Frequency: {!Product__c.Payment_Frequency__c}
Proposed Donation: {!Product__c.Proposed_Donation_Rate__c}
Expected First disbursement date: {!Product__c.Expected_First_disbursement_date__c}

Upon review we can confirm that we will {!Product__c.Proposal_Status__c} the Debt Management Proposal for the customer under the following terms:
Current Balance: {!Product__c.Current_Balance__c}
Accepted Interest rate: {!Product__c.Accepted_Interest_rate__c}
Accepted Payment Amount:{!Product__c.Accepted_Payment_Amount__c}
Payment Frequency: {!Product__c.Payment_Frequency__c}
Accepted Donation Rate: {!Product__c.Accepted_Donation_Rate__c}
Expected First Disbursement Date: {!Product__c.Expected_First_disbursement_date__c}
Date of last payment: {!product__c.Payment_Created__c}
Amount of last payment: {!Product__c.Payment_Amount__c}
Reason for Decline: {!Product__c.Proposal_Reject_Reason__c}

1. If the creditor has agreed to pay your organization a donation which is set out in the terms above, then please deduct the donation per the Creditors accepted donation rate from each payment.
2. Personal cheques from customers will not be accepted.
3. The above noted account number must be provided on ALL payments to ensure accuracy of processing the payments.
4. If no payments are received for 3 consecutive months, the proposed terms will be deemed to be in default and the proposal null and void.
5. Please ensure all payments are made payable to Canaccede International Management Ltd.


Sincerely,

{!CCSPackage.CFG_Name__c}
{!CCSPackage.CFG_Office_Name__c}
{!servicerName}












